  "summary": "Security update for the Linux Kernel (Live Patch 54 for SLE 15 SP3)",
  "details": "This update for the Linux Kernel 5.3.18-150300_59_195 fixes several issues.\n\nThe following security issues were fixed:\n\n- CVE-2022-49080: mm/mempolicy: fix mpol_new leak in shared_policy_replace (bsc#1238324).\n- CVE-2024-57996: net_sched: sch_sfq: do not allow 1 packet limit (bsc#1239077).\n- CVE-2022-49563: crypto: qat - add param check for RSA (bsc#1238788).\n- CVE-2022-49564: crypto: qat - add param check for DH (bsc#1238790).\n",
